<D>__{sugar creek! that was a long time ago, but it's all coming back to me now. there was another merit badge you could get for roller skating. there used to be a roller rink at a bend in sugar creek, up above where the sewage went in. i got in a fight there one time. i had on roller skates, and the guy i was fighting had on basketball shoes. he had a tremendous advantage over me. he was a little guy, but he beat the shit out of me. i had to laugh like hell. don't ever fight a guy when you've got on roller skates.}
