<A>__{blackout.}
<B>__{scene seven}
<A>__{silence. pitch blackness. the sounds of a nazi rally come up slowly: "sieg heil! sieg heil! sieg heil!" spotlight comes up on major siegfried von konigswald, and officer in the dreaded ss. he is in full ceremonial uniform. the sounds fade.}
<C>__{von konigswald}
